{"word":"H3231 - יָמַן - yâman - yaw-man' - Go to the right hand","slug":"H3231","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָמַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yâman"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yaw-man'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Go to the right hand"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05DE;&#x05DF; - ya&#x0302;man</b> - <i>yaw-man'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>be</i> (physically) <i>right</i> (that is, firm); but used only as denominative from <a href=\"#/H3225\">H3225</a> and transitively, to <i>be right handed</i> or <i>take the right hand</i> side: - go (turn) to (on, use) the right hand."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3225\">H3225</a>, <a href=\"#/H3226\">H3226</a>, <a href=\"#/H3227\">H3227</a>, <a href=\"#/H3228\">H3228</a>, <a href=\"#/H3232\">H3232</a>, <a href=\"#/H3233\">H3233</a>, <a href=\"#/H541\">H541</a>, <a href=\"#/H8486\">H8486</a>, <a href=\"#/H8487\">H8487</a>, <a href=\"#/H8488\">H8488</a>, <a href=\"#/H8489\">H8489</a>"}]}